data.description: This charming tri-level home nestled in the highly coveted Morningside community in Santee offers a spacious layout with 4 bedrooms, 4 full baths, and hickory flooring throughout the main living space. Featuring a first-floor bedroom with an attached bathroom, W/D room, dual patios, 2-car garage and an open concept kitchen/family room/dining room, it's perfect for both relaxation and entertaining. With amenities such as community playgrounds, pool w/ spa and BBQ areas. Gated and with Low HOA,  VA approved. Don't wait, seize the opportunity to make this your dream home today!
